Investment Performance Analytics: Track the performance of your gold investments over time. Visualize gains and losses with detailed charts.

Alerts and Notifications: Set custom alerts for market price changes, reminders for potential selling opportunities, and notifications for significant market news.

Secure Storage: Use high-level encryption to secure sensitive data about your gold investments. Optionally, integrate biometric authentication for an extra layer of security.

Portfolio Diversification Insights: Suggestions for diversifying your gold holdings based on current market conditions and your investment goals.

